{"content": "<h2>The Duality of Life</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Roya often contrasts her inner world with the outer world everyone else sees. That juxtaposition is achieved deftly through the amalgamation of a multi-faceted character of self.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"677\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/inner-monologue-and-outer-presence-1024x925.jpeg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/inner-monologue-and-outer-presence-1024x925.jpeg 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/inner-monologue-and-outer-presence-300x271.jpeg 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/inner-monologue-and-outer-presence-768x694.jpeg 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/inner-monologue-and-outer-presence-1536x1388.jpeg 1536w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/inner-monologue-and-outer-presence-1320x1192.jpeg 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/inner-monologue-and-outer-presence-600x542.jpeg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/inner-monologue-and-outer-presence.jpeg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Dance of duality by Roya</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t“We are both dark and light, hidden and revealed, bound together in a perpetual dance of duality.”\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>Roya</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t<p>Roya first joined the cryptoart revolution 1325 days ago so is no stranger to the world of minted art. A featured artist in the <a href=\"https://theline.wtf/crypto-books/\">MINTED book</a> the first introduction to her line work. </p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"562\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/roya-minted-book-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/roya-minted-book-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/roya-minted-book-300x225.jpg 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/roya-minted-book-768x576.jpg 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/roya-minted-book-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/roya-minted-book-2048x1536.jpg 2048w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/roya-minted-book-400x300.jpg 400w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/roya-minted-book-1320x990.jpg 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/roya-minted-book-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t<p>Roya refers to her art practice as one that conveys freedom and powerful emotions. The symbolic forms of freedom are clear to see through the wings of butterfly, the free flowing hair and the often cosmically  arranged portraits.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\"She never looked away. Tears streaming down her cheek, filling the dark places inside with the blood of the mother. Flowers grow here, deep inside her heart. Her eyes wide open, pierce through the veil and fixate on the horizon. She knows where she is going, she knows who she is, she asks not for permission and lives beyond regrets.\nLook into her depths, what do you see?\"\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>Roya on Eye Contact</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t<p>The search for identity through who we know ourselves to be versus how others perceive us are in constant dialogue in Roya's work. Some of her most powerful work is represented through what is not shown. </p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"787\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-warriors-soul-roya-975x1024.jpg\" alt=\"A warrior&#039;s soul roya\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-warriors-soul-roya-975x1024.jpg 975w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-warriors-soul-roya-286x300.jpg 286w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-warriors-soul-roya-768x806.jpg 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-warriors-soul-roya-1463x1536.jpg 1463w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-warriors-soul-roya-1320x1386.jpg 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-warriors-soul-roya-600x630.jpg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-warriors-soul-roya.jpg 1800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>A Warrior's Soul</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t<p>In 'A Warrior's Soul' the subject is cut in half and a memorial flower placed in lieu of the full human experience, hands covering her face. </p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\"Her demands for freedom wasn’t in words , it was a silent protest of living by example.\nThis illustration is inspired by' Golshifteh Farahani' and her revolutionary story.\"\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>Roya</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t\t<h2>Immense Vulnerability</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>The female form is turned into a political instrument where the viewer is forced to deal with the beauty of natural form lost to imposing elements of sorrow and pain. That combination is what shifts Roya's work beyond mere form into the kind of work that sparks movements.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"749\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/superraremahsaamini-1024x1024.jpeg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/superraremahsaamini-1024x1024.jpeg 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/superraremahsaamini-300x300.jpeg 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/superraremahsaamini-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/superraremahsaamini-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/superraremahsaamini-1536x1536.jpeg 1536w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/superraremahsaamini-2048x2048.jpeg 2048w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/superraremahsaamini-400x400.jpeg 400w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/superraremahsaamini-1320x1320.jpeg 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/superraremahsaamini-600x600.jpeg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/superraremahsaamini-100x100.jpeg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Mahsa Amini</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t<p>You can find more of Roya's work in her dedicated exhibition on The Line 165.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://theline.wtf/listing/roya/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tRoya | Line 165 \n\t\t\t\t\t</a>"}